<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 12:23:58 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>瑞典第七AP基金不包括沙特阿美公司和其他六家公司</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/swedens-seventh-ap-fund-excludes-saudi-aramco-six-other-companies-2024-06-03/</link><description>瑞典第七 AP 基金 (AP7) 养老基金经理周一表示，由于石油开采或煤炭生产领域的大规模业务，该基金已将沙特阿美公司和其他六家公司从其投资组合中列入黑名单。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 11:45:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/swedens-seventh-ap-fund-excludes-saudi-aramco-six-other-companies-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>工党发言人在英国上市前会见了 Shein</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/labour-party-has-met-with-shein-ahead-potential-uk-listing-spokesperson-2024-06-03/</link><description>人们普遍预计将在英国下一次选举中掌权的工党表示，在伦敦上市之前，工党已与中国创办的快时尚制造商 Shein 进行了会面。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 11:26:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/labour-party-has-met-with-shein-ahead-potential-uk-listing-spokesperson-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰战争：瑞士基辅和平条款峰会有何期待</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/what-expect-swiss-summit-ukraines-peace-terms-2024-06-03/</link><description>瑞士将于6月15日至16日主办峰会，旨在为乌克兰总统泽连斯基的和平提议争取广泛的国际支持，其中包括俄罗斯军队从乌克兰全面撤军，但莫斯科尚未受到邀请。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 10:37:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/what-expect-swiss-summit-ukraines-peace-terms-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：华尔街关注充满选举的六月就业周</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-06-03/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 10:03:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>尽管伊朗愤怒，中国仍坚持对有争议的海湾岛屿的立场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-maintains-stance-disputed-gulf-islands-despite-irans-anger-2024-06-03/</link><description>尽管德黑兰对北京将伊朗控制的岛屿描述为需要与阿拉伯联合酋长国解决的问题感到愤怒，但中国周一在波斯湾的三个有争议的岛屿上保持了立场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 09:23:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-maintains-stance-disputed-gulf-islands-despite-irans-anger-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示所有努力都应在俄乌和平措施中得到认可</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/china-says-all-efforts-should-be-recognised-russia-ukraine-peace-measures-2024-06-03/</link><description>中国外交部发言人周一表示，中方认为，支持围绕俄乌战争采取和平措施的一切努力都应得到认可。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 08:22:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/china-says-all-efforts-should-be-recognised-russia-ukraine-peace-measures-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>腾讯、腾讯音乐拟7000万美元入股泰国GMM音乐10%股权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/tencent-tencent-music-value-thailands-gmm-music-700-mln-with-stake-buy-2024-06-03/</link><description>泰国娱乐平台GMM Music周一表示，腾讯和腾讯音乐娱乐将以7000万美元收购该公司10%的股份，巩固其分拆计划。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 06:28:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/tencent-tencent-music-value-thailands-gmm-music-700-mln-with-stake-buy-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>继中国之后，Zara 将直播购物实验扩展到欧洲和美国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/after-china-zara-expands-live-shopping-experiment-europe-us-2024-06-03/</link><description>Zara今年将把直播购物扩展到英国、欧洲和美国，测试一种在中国已经广受欢迎但西方购物者不太熟悉的模式。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 05:10:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/after-china-zara-expands-live-shopping-experiment-europe-us-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：工厂繁忙，市场情绪乐观</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-06-03/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 04:35:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>5月份工厂活动出现复苏迹象</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-economy-asian-factory-activity-expands-may-robust-global-demand-2024-06-03/</link><description>周一的私营企业调查显示，随着欧元区收缩放缓以及大多数亚洲最大经济体的制造业活动回升，全球工厂活动上个月出现复苏迹象。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 03:08:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-economy-asian-factory-activity-expands-may-robust-global-demand-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟专员表示，欧盟提议的俄罗斯液化天然气转运禁令不会给亚洲带来任何问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/proposed-eu-ban-russian-lng-transhipments-pose-no-problems-asia-eu-commissioner-2024-06-03/</link><description>欧盟能源委员卡德里·西姆森周一在东京对记者表示，针对俄罗斯液化天然气（LNG）转运的欧洲新制裁提议不太可能影响亚洲买家。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 02:44:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/proposed-eu-ban-russian-lng-transhipments-pose-no-problems-asia-eu-commissioner-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>印度莫迪计划大选后改革以与中国制造业竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-modi-plans-post-election-reforms-rival-chinese-manufacturing-2024-06-03/</link><description>据两名知情政府官员透露，如果印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪本周赢得第三个任期，他计划采取一系列有利于商业的措施，包括推动制定法规，使雇用和解雇工人变得更容易。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 02:04:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-modi-plans-post-election-reforms-rival-chinese-manufacturing-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>财新PMI显示中国制造业激增，但全球风险增加</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-growth-hits-2-year-high-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-06-03/</link><description>周一的一项私营部门调查显示，由于产量增长和新订单，特别是小型企业的新订单，中国5月份工厂活动增长约两年来最快，提振了第二季度的前景。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 01:49:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-growth-hits-2-year-high-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>交易员思考美联储前景，美元走高；关注欧洲央行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/currencies-tread-cautiously-after-us-inflation-report-focus-ecb-2024-06-03/</link><description>美元周一保持稳定，因投资者认为美国通胀可能已放缓至足以让美联储在 2024 年降息，而欧元在欧洲央行本周预期降息之前保持平静。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 01:37:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/currencies-tread-cautiously-after-us-inflation-report-focus-ecb-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲股市上涨，关注欧洲央行利率变动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-03/</link><description>欧洲股市周一反弹，政府债券收益率下跌，因投资者期待欧洲央行降息，而本周公布的美国就业数据则将焦点集中在通胀上。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 00:46:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-03/</guid></item></channel></rss>